-- Edcon Division Head Resigns in South Africa, Independent Says
-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 2012-05-13T09:25:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-13/edcon-division-head-resigns-in-south-africa-independent-says.html
Hugues Witvoet, the chief executive
officer of a division of Bain Capital LLC-controlled Edcon
Holdings (Pty) Ltd., resigned with effect of May 9, the
Johannesburg-based Sunday Independent reported, citing the
company. No reasons for the resignation were given.  Telephone calls today by Bloomberg News to Edcon’s offices
went unanswered outside of normal working hours. Phone calls to
Jaqui Cameron, a spokeswoman for the company, and investor
relations manager Tessa Christelis didn’t connect.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  